{
  "html": "<h2 data-idx=\"0\">Sample Credit Agreement</h2>\n<p data-idx=\"1\">This  Credit  Agreement  is  entered  into  as  of  January  1,  2024,  by  and  between  XYZ  Corporation  (the Borrower) and ABC Bank (the Lender).</p>\n<h2 data-idx=\"2\">Article I - Definitions</h2>\n<table data-idx=\"3\"><tr><th>Term</th><th>Definition</th></tr>\n<tr><td>Borrower</td><td>XYZ Corporation, a Delaware corporation</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Commitment</td><td>The aggregate amount of $50,000,000</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Maturity Date</td><td>January 1, 2029</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Interest Rate</td><td>Base Rate plus 2.00% per annum</td></tr></table>\n<p data-idx=\"4\">Section 1.1. The following terms have the meanings set forth below:</p>\n<h2 data-idx=\"5\">Article II - Representations</h2>\n<p data-idx=\"6\">The Borrower represents that it is a corporation duly organized, validly existing, and in good standing under the laws of the State of Delaware.</p>\n<h2 data-idx=\"7\">Signatures</h2>\n<p data-idx=\"8\">XYZ Corporation</p>\n<p data-idx=\"9\">By: _________________________</p>\n<p data-idx=\"10\">Name: John Executive</p>\n<p data-idx=\"11\">Title: Chief Executive Officer</p>",
